 PL-4 (1)   SECURITY AND PRIVACY ARCHITECTURES | DEFENSE IN DEPTH


No OT Discussion for this control.
Control Enhancement: (1) OT Discussion: Defense in depth is considered a common practice for
security architecture within OT environments.
